    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. The 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, delivering razor-sharp throttle response through its individual throttle bodies and perfectly synchronized Double VANOS system. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is impeccable, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a completely stock suspension geometry that retains its original damping characteristics. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is accounted for, ensuring a visceral, analog driving experience free of NVH issues. This is a collector-tier specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
