      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector-tier condition. This example features the S54 inline-six powerhouse, boasting its original individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline with perfect harmonic balance. The valvetrain has been meticulously maintained with documented Vanos bulletproofing and recent valve lash adjustments. The drivetrain utilizes a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, feeding power through a reinforced subframe to the GKN limited-slip differential. Suspension kinematics are factory-sharp, featuring refreshed bushings and pristine dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage is free of any galvanic corrosion or fluid weepage. A mechanically flawless specimen for the serious driver.",
